OL,3,CGodzilla vs. Kong actor Kaylee Hottle
OL,4,Ckilled in car crash at 18
OL,6,FKaylee Hottle, a deaf actor best known
OL,7,Ffor her starring role in two Godzilla
OL,8,Ffilms, has died in a car crash aged 18.
OL,10,FThe American performer was one of two
OL,11,Fpassengers in the car when it went off
OL,12,Fthe road and hit a culvert in
OL,13,FIjamsville, Maryland shortly before
OL,14,F3am, police said.
OL,16,FThe driver, aged 19, was taken to a
OL,17,Flocal hospital with non-life-
OL,18,Fthreatening injuries, and the other
OL,19,Fpassenger declined medical treatment,
OL,20,Faccording to a statement by Frederick
OL,21,FCounty Sheriff's Office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
