OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784719105
OL,3,CGodzilla vs. Kong actor Kaylee Hottle
OL,4,Ckilled in car crash at 18
OL,6,FSpeed is believed to be a factor in
OL,7,Fthe crash, which is under
OL,8,Finvestigation, the statement added.
OL,10,FHottle, who appeared in Godzilla Vs.
OL,11,FKong and its sequel Godzilla X Kong:
OL,12,FThe New Empire, was a native signer of
OL,13,FAmerican Sign Language, and her family
OL,14,Fmembers are also deaf.
OL,16,F"Privilege to be your mom, Kaylee
OL,17,FHottle," the actor's mother Ketsi
OL,18,FHottle wrote on social media, while
OL,19,Fher father Joshua posted: "I am taking
OL,20,Fa flight I would never like to take."
