OL,3,CGodzilla vs. Kong actor Kaylee Hottle
OL,4,Ckilled in car crash at 18
OL,6,FIn the two Godzilla movies she starred
OL,7,Fin, Hottle played an orphaned girl
OL,8,Fnamed Jia who sees beyond Kong's
OL,9,Fthreatening appearance and forms a
OL,10,Fspecial bond with the monster,
OL,11,Fcommunicating with him using sign
OL,12,Flanguage.
OL,14,F"I'm so devastated to hear this. You
OL,15,Fwill be deeply missed Kaylee," her
OL,16,F"Godzilla" co-star Millie Bobby Brown,
OL,17,Fposted on Instagram, sharing a black
OL,18,Fand white image of Hottle on the app.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@^O]xD@AOUxD@JO]
