OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784719105
OL,3,CGodzilla vs. Kong actor Kaylee Hottle
OL,4,Ckilled in car crash at 18
OL,6,FMarlee Matlin, who was the first deaf
OL,7,Factress to win an Oscar for her role
OL,8,Fin Children Of A Lesser God, shared a
OL,9,Fphoto to X of herself alongside Hottle.
OL,11,FShe wrote: "I am absolutely gutted
OL,12,Fabout the passing of sweet Kaylee
OL,13,FHottle. May her beauty and talent be a
OL,14,Fmemory for eternity."
OL,16,FHottle attended Texas School For The
OL,17,FDeaf (TSD) in Austin, where she was a
OL,18,Fsenior, and the institution has paid
OL,19,Ftribute to her after the
OL,20,F"heartbreaking" news of her death.
OL,26,@sD@LOUvD@UO]|D@AOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
