OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784719105
OL,3,CGodzilla vs. Kong actor Kaylee Hottle
OL,4,Ckilled in car crash at 18
OL,6,FThe school shared a photo of her and
OL,7,Fwrote: "It is with profound sadness
OL,8,Fthat we share the heartbreaking news
OL,9,Fthat one of our TSD seniors, Kaylee
OL,10,FHottle, tragically passed away
OL,11,Fyesterday in a car accident in
OL,12,FFrederick, Maryland.
OL,14,F"Our hearts are with Kaylee's family,
OL,15,Ffriends, classmates, and everyone who
OL,16,Fknew and loved her during this
OL,17,Fincredibly difficult time."
OL,19,FIt added: "Please keep Kaylee's loved
OL,20,Fones in your thoughts as we mourn this
OL,21,Ftremendous loss together."
OL,26,@oD@HOUvD@AOUyD@[O]{D@KOU}D@ZO]
