OL,3,CGodzilla vs. Kong actor Kaylee Hottle
OL,4,Ckilled in car crash at 18
OL,6,FFollowing her appearance in Godzilla X
OL,7,FKong, Hottle received a Saturn Award
OL,8,Fnomination for best performance by a
OL,9,Fyounger actor.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FWhile promoting the hit sci-fi films,
OL,17,Fthe actress often spoke about the
OL,18,Finclusion of deafness in the
OL,19,Fentertainment industry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
