OL,3,CGodzilla vs. Kong actor Kaylee Hottle
OL,4,Ckilled in car crash at 18
OL,6,FHottle has also appeared in a 2021
OL,7,Fepisode of Magnum PI, as well as
OL,8,Fseveral advertisements ` including one
OL,9,Fpromoting support for the deaf
OL,10,Fcommunity in their pursuit of equal
OL,11,Frights.
OL,13,FShe was also listed as appearing in
OL,14,Fthe upcoming film "What Doesn't Kill
OL,15,FUs".
OL,17,FIn a post on Instagram, Alaqua Cox,
OL,18,Fher co-star in that film and fellow
OL,19,Fdeaf actor, said: "I'm so heartbroken.
OL,20,FMy heart goes out to her family during
OL,21,Fthis unimaginable time."
